\c 10
\s Ukuthunywa kwabafundi abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa
\p
\v 1 Njalo emva kwalezizinto iNkosi yamisa njalo abanye\x + 9.1,2,6. 9.52. 23.32.\x* abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + Eks. 24.1,9. Nani 11.16.\x*, yabathuma ngababili phambi kobuso bayo emizini yonke lezindaweni zonke ebizakuya kuzo yona\x + Mat. 10.1. Mark. 6.7.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho yathi kubo: Isibili isivuno sikhulu, kodwa izisebenzi zinlutshwana. Ngakho ncengani eNkosini yesivuno, ukuze ithume izisebenzi esivunweni sayo\x + Mat. 9.37,38.\x*.
\v 3 Hambani; khangelani, mina ngiyalithuma linjengezimvana phakathi kwezimpisi\x + Mat. 10.16.\x*.
\v 4 Lingaphathi\x + Mat. 10.9-15. Mark. 6.8-11. Luka 9.3-5.\x* umxhaka, lesikhwama, lamanyathela\x + 12.33. 22.35,36.\x*; njalo lingabingeleli muntu endleleni\x + 2 Kho. 4.29.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo lakuyiphi indlu elingena kuyo, qalani lithi: Ukuthula \add kakube\add* kulindlu\x + 1 Sam. 25.6. Luka 24.36.\x*.
\v 6 Njalo uba kukhona lapho indodana yokuthula, ukuthula kwenu kuzahlala phezu kwayo\x + 16.8. Joha. 12.36. Efe. 2.2. 5.6,8. Kol. 3.6. 1 Thes. 5.5. Joha. 17.12. 2 Thes. 2.3.\x*; kodwa uba kunge\add njalo\add*, kuzabuyela kini.
\v 7 Hlalani-ke kuleyondlu, lidle linathe izinto ezivela kubo; ngoba isisebenzi sifanele umvuzo waso. Lingayi endlini lendlini.
\v 8 Lakuwuphi umuzi elingena kuwo, besebelemukela, dlanini okubekwa phambi kwenu\x + 11.6. 1 Kor. 10.27.\x*,
\v 9 lisilise abagulayo abakuwo\x + 9.2. Mat. 10.7,8.\x*, njalo lithi kubo: Umbuso kaNkulunkulu usondele kini\x + 10.11. Mat. 3.2.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa lakuwuphi umuzi elingena kuwo, futhi bengalemukeli, phumelani endleleni zawo, lithi:
\v 11 Lothuli lomuzi wenu olusinamatheleyo siyaluthintithela kini\x + Seb. 13.51.\x*; kodwa-ke yazini lokhu, ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu usondele kini\x + 9.11. Mat. 3.2.\x*.
\v 12 Njalo ngithi kini: Kuzakuba lula eSodoma ngalolosuku, kulakulowomuzi\x + 10.14. Mat. 10.15. Mark. 6.11.\x*.
\s Ukusolwa kwemizi engaphendukanga
\p
\v 13 Maye kuwe, Korazini! Maye kuwe, Bhethisayida! Ngoba uba kwakwenziwe eTire leSidoni imisebenzi yamandla eyenziwe kini\x + Mat. 11.21-23.\x*, ngabe kade baphenduka bahlala emasakeni lemlotheni\x + Jobe 2.8. Jona 3.6.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa kuzakuba lula eTire leSidoni ekugwetshweni, kulakini\x + 10.14. Mat. 10.15. Mark. 6.11.\x*.
\v 15 Lawe, Kapenawume, ophakanyiselwe ezulwini, uzaphoselwa phansi esihogweni.
\p
\v 16 Olizwayo lina uyangizwa mina\x + Mat. 10.40.\x*; lolalayo lina uyangala mina\x + Joha. 12.48. 1 Thes. 4.8. Mark. 7.9.\x*; longalayo mina uyamala ongithumileyo\x + Joha. 5.23.\x*.
\s Ukubuya kwabangamatshumi ayisikhombisa
\p
\v 17 Babuya-ke abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa ngentokozo\x + 10.1.\x*, besithi: Nkosi, lamadimoni ayazehlisela ngaphansi kwethu ebizweni lakho\x + Mark. 16.17.\x*.
\v 18 Wasesithi kubo: Ngabona uSathane njengombane\x + Joha. 12.31.\x* esiwa evela ezulwini\x + Isam. 12.8,12. Isa. 14.12.\x*.
\v 19 Khangelani, ngilinika amandla okunyathela phezu kwezinyoka labofezela, laphezu kwamandla wonke esitha; njalo akusoze kube lalutho olungalilimaza\x + Hlab. 91.13. Mark. 16.18. Seb. 28.5. Luka 11.12.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa lingathokozi ngalokho ukuthi omoya bayazehlisela ngaphansi kwenu\x + Mat. 7.22,23.\x*; kodwa ikakhulu thokozani ukuthi amabizo enu alotshiwe emazulwini\x + Eks. 32.32. Isa. 4.3. Heb. 12.23. Jer. 17.13.\x*.
\s UJesu ubonga uYise
\p
\v 21 Ngalelohola uJesu\x + 10.21,22, Mat. 11.25-27.\x* wathokoza emoyeni\x + Isa. 53.11.\x*, wathi: Ngiyakubonga, Baba, Nkosi yezulu lomhlaba, ngoba uzifihlile lezizinto kwabahlakaniphileyo labaqedisisayo, kodwa wazembulela izingane; yebo, Baba, ngoba ngokunjalo kwaba kuhle phambi kwakho\x + 12.32. 2.14.\x*.
\v 22 Konke kwanikelwa kimi nguBaba; njalo kakho owaziyo ukuthi iNdodana ingubani, ngaphandle kukaBaba, lokuthi uBaba ungubani, ngaphandle kweNdodana, njalo loba ngubani iNdodana ethanda ukumembulela.
\p
\v 23 Wasephendukela kubafundi bebodwa wathi: Abusisiwe amehlo abona elikubonayo.
\v 24 Ngoba ngithi kini: Abaprofethi abanengi lamakhosi babethanda ukubona izinto elizibonayo lina, kodwa kaba\add zi\add*bonanga; lokuzwa izinto elizizwayo, kodwa kaba\add zi\add*zwanga\x + 10.23,24, Mat. 13.16,17.\x*.
\s Umlayo wokuqala
\p
\v 25 Njalo khangela, isazumthetho esithile\x + Mat. 22.35.\x* sasesisukuma, simlinga\x + Joha. 6.6. Joha. 8.6.\x*, sisithi: Mfundisi, ngenzeni ukuze ngidle ilifa lempilo elaphakade\x + Mat. 19.16. Mark. 10.17. Luka 18.18. Mat. 22.35-39.\x*?
\v 26 Wasesithi kuso: Kubhalweni emlayweni? Uwubala njani?
\v 27 Sasesiphendula sathi: Wothanda iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho, ngenhliziyo yakho yonke, langomphefumulo wakho wonke, langamandla akho wonke, langengqondo yakho yonke\x + Dute. 6.5.\x*; lomakhelwane wakho njengalokhu uzi\add thanda wena\x + Levi 19.18.\x*\add*.
\v 28 Wasesithi kuso: Uphendule ngokuqonda; yenza lokhu, futhi uzaphila\x + Levi 18.5. Neh. 9.29.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso womSamariya olesihawu
\p
\v 29 Kodwa sona sithanda ukuzilungisisa\x + 16.15.\x* sathi kuJesu: Kanti ngubani umakhelwane wami?
\v 30 UJesu wasephendula wathi: Umuntu othile wehla evela eJerusalema\x + 2.42. 18.31. 19.28.\x* esiya eJeriko\x + Josh. 16.1. Mat. 20.29.\x*, watheleka phakathi kwabaphangi\x + 10.36. Mat. 26.55.\x*, njalo bamhlubula impahla ba\add m\add*tshaya imivimvinya basuka bahamba, ba\add m\add*tshiya ephosukufa.
\v 31 Umpristi othile waseqabuka esehla ngaleyondlela\x + 2.42. 18.31. 19.28.\x*; njalo wathi embona, wadlula eceleni\x + Hlab. 38.11.\x*.
\v 32 Langokunjalo lomLevi nxa wayesekulindawo, wafika e\add m\add*bona, wadlula eceleni\x + Hlab. 38.11.\x*.
\v 33 Kodwa umSamariya\x + Mat. 10.5.\x* othile owayehamba wafika lapho ayekhona, njalo kwathi embona waba lesihelo,
\v 34 waya \add kuye\add* wabopha amanxeba akhe\x + Isa. 1.6.\x*, ewathela amagcobo lewayini\x + Isa. 1.6.\x*; wamkhweza phezu kweyakhe inyamazana, wamusa endlini yezihambi, wamlondoloza.
\v 35 Kusisa esehamba, wakhupha \w odenariyo\w** ababili wa\add ba\add*nika umninindlu, wathi kuye: Umlondoloze; njalo loba yini ozakuchitha okwedlula lokhu, mina ngizabuyisela kuwe ekubuyeni kwami.
\v 36 Pho, nguwuphi kulaba abathathu ocabanga ukuthi wayengumakhelwane walowo owatheleka phakathi kwabaphangi\x + 10.36. Mat. 26.55.\x*?
\v 37 Wasesithi: Ngulowo owamenzela isihawu\x + 1.72.\x*. Ngakho uJesu wathi kuye: Hamba, lawe wenze njalo.
\s UMarta loMariya
\p
\v 38 Kwasekusithi ekuhambeni kwabo, yena wangena emzaneni othile; lowesifazana othile, uMarta\x + 10.40,41. Joha. 11.1,5,19,20,21,24,30,39. 12.2.\x* ngebizo, wamemukela endlini yakhe\x + 19.6. Seb. 17.7. Jak. 2.25.\x*.
\v 39 Njalo lo wayelodadewabo othiwa nguMariya\x + 10.42. Joha. 11.1,2,19,20,28,31,32,45. 12.3.\x*, laye owahlala enyaweni zikaJesu\x + 8.35. 2 Kho. 4.38. Joha. 11.20.\x*, walizwa ilizwi lakhe.
\v 40 Kodwa uMarta wayephazanyiswa yikusebenza okunengi\x + 10.40,41. Joha. 11.1,5,19,20,21,24,30,39. 12.2.\x*; weza eduze wasesithi: Nkosi, kawukhathali yini ukuthi udadewethu ungitshiye ukuthi ngisebenze ngedwa? Ngakho umtshele ukuthi angisize.
\v 41 Kodwa uJesu waphendula wathi kuye: Marta, Marta\x + 10.40,41. Joha. 11.1,5,19,20,21,24,30,39. 12.2.\x*, uyaphiseka ukhathazeke ngezinto ezinengi\x + Mat. 6.25. Luka 12.11. 1 Kor. 7.32.\x*;
\v 42 kodwa yinye into edingekayo\x + Joha. 6.27. Hlab. 27.4.\x*; kodwa uMariya ukhethile isabelo esihle, angayikwemukwa sona\x + Hlab. 16.5.\x*.
